name: Kim-Hue Popular Library Fundraising - Special Edition
description:
100 % of the sales will go to the Kim-Hue Popular Library.
This popular library is located in the Gas Plant neighborhood of the city of Trelew in Patagonia Argentina. Adolescent, children and mothers come together in bulnerable situations, at the library they are given school support, food and the possibility of generating work. But the most important thing is that it works as an integrator from the neighborhood to the city and as a place of containment for children who live under risk situations.
